transcripts: Rug doctor developed our line of platinum and antibacterial carpet cleaner sprays to give you professional quality results and peace of mind. Each spray perfect for keeping soft surfaces clean between deep cleanings including carpets, mattresses, couches, pet beds, car seats, area rugs and more and they're all safe for pets and kids. Platinum urine Eliminator spray uses Pro enzymatic action to eliminate pet stains and odors. The patented odor neutralizer also discourage your pets from remarking keeping it cleaner longer. Platinum spot and stain remover has been scientifically engineered to deep clean and prolong the life of soft surfaces. Use platinum spot and stain remover to treat stains created by wine, food, mud, grease and more. Finally antibacterial carpet cleaner kills 99% of bacteria and eliminates common allergens it can be used on everyday items like bedspreads, gym bags, diaper bags and pet beds. Life happens keep these three sprays on hand to clean, sanitized and deodorize whatever comes your way. Let's get cleaning.
